              },
              {
                "value": "C4",
                "time": 2,
                "duration": 1
              },
              {
                "value": "B4",
                "time": 5,
                "duration": 1
              },
              {
                "value": "C5",
                "time": 6,
                "duration": 2
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "instrument": "drum",
            "notes": []
          }
        ],
        "timeLength": 12,
        "currentTrack": "piano",
        "bpm": 90,
        "keyboardOctave": 4
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "可以看到，我们并没有改变每个音的音高，只是简单将每个音的时间做了调整，就会呈现出很不一样的效果，这种对音符时间的规划，就是我们经常提到的“节奏”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "我们再来尝试一次"
        }
      ]
